    @CreoleResource(name="BulStem",
                helpURL="http://lml.bas.bg/~nakov/bulstem/",
                comment="This plugin is an implementation of the BulStem stemmer algorithm for Bulgarian developed by Preslav Nakov.")
public class BulStemPR
extends gate.creole.AbstractLanguageAnalyser
implements gate.ProcessingResource, Serializable
    Stemming algorithm by Preslav Nakov.
    Author:
    Alexander Alexandrov, e-mail: sencko@mail.bg, provided the JAVA implementation of the algorithm, Ivelina Nikolova, e-mail:iva@lml.bas.bg, wrapped the stemmer for GATE
